Package com.preemptive.instrumentation Description

Accessing this documentation inside Eclipse

  • Copy a version of the PA jar to your Eclipse project and add it to the Build Path.
  • From the Libraries tab in the Build Path dialog click on the PA jar and open its property tree.li
  • Click on the Javadoc property entry and then click on the Edit button.
  • Enter the location where this Javadoc is installed into the Javadoc location path entry.
  • Click Validate to verify the setting is correct.

Additional information can be found in the Eclipse documentation.
